Monitoring:
- Setup monitoring for services / ports / files / etc
- Email alerts when criteria are met
- Jabber alerts
- Update page/file on server

tools:
- ping (min/max/avg over 10)
- traceroute (ip, host, network, ping)
- snmp

benchmarks:
- apache benchmark (ab)
- ...

apache status (mod_status)
- /server-status?refresh=N (seconds)
<Location /server-status>
SetHandler server-status
ExtendedStatus On
- /server-info
- uptime
- cpu%
- mem%

system: 
- uptime
- load
- cpu
- mem

filesystem:
- usage / free

php:
- phpinfo() data

Order Deny,Allow
Deny from all
Allow from .foo.com
</Location>

marketting:
- SEO score (number of keywords, number of backlinks, page rank, page size, has title/keywords/description, has only 1 h1 tag)
- net worth
http://websitevalued.com/MarketPlace.aspx
- daily page views
- daily ads revenue

- text browser (h1 in red, links in bold)

- title relevancy
- description relevancy
- terms (unique / linked)
